Attention mechanism:  this paper pro-poses a new model based on BERT and deep learning for Weibo text sentiment analysis. Specifically, first using BERT to represent the text with dynamic word vectors and using the processed sentiment dictionary to enhance the sentiment features of the vectors; then adopting the BiLSTM to extract the contextual features of the text, the processed vector representation is weighted by the attention mechanism.
